{"tid":915583,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做飲食業好慘","createTime":"2018-11-25T05:56:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T13:40:07.000Z","uid":201694,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"428b3234d88b5ec7d6a02521456cce4433e21761","tid":915583,"uid":201694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T05:56:40.000Z","msg":"成日都要望住班客係到食野 <br />\n但自己就有排都未放得飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前試過要4點幾先有得放晏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要成比班客催同呼呼喝喝<br />\n但明明出野出得慢我都控制唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咁催廚房又比人炆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人有同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c085a736ecbc036fcc2d384cf11e8666bcfc4ff5","tid":915583,"uid":195920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T06:02:27.000Z","msg":"星期六日要返工"},{"pid":"b02bc169d13ab5762dee7887c04cd21963197686","tid":915583,"uid":201694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c085a736ecbc036fcc2d384cf11e8666bcfc4ff5","tid":915583,"uid":195920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T06:02:27.000Z","msg":"星期六日要返工"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T06:09:48.000Z","msg":"忙到乜又餓到乜咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad46140feacfad101650e11d554fd2b4e038f59a","tid":915583,"uid":182397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T06:10:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e47d7efc91829ea6f485ec2fefcb9c529c112af8","tid":915583,"uid":182397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T06:11:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"65804ba72f8a3787fa862de7fbe7de1622d6fd2e","tid":915583,"uid":201694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e47d7efc91829ea6f485ec2fefcb9c529c112af8","tid":915583,"uid":182397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-2